    "bookOrder": 230,
    "summary": "从家常食物唤起的记忆，理解食物与情感的联系。"
  },
  "sentences": [
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s1",
      "text": "Delicious memories",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p1",
      "tr": "美味的记忆",
      "g": "形容词 + 名词",
      "d": "名词短语作为标题，概括文章主题。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/kJuZsRWyJDVsQkt82YSV8o.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s2",
      "text": "The taste and smell of a certain food can often bring back memories.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p1",
      "tr": "某种食物的味道和气味往往能勾起回忆。",
      "g": "主语 (The taste and smell...) + 情态动词 (can) + 谓语 (bring back) + 宾语 (memories)",
      "d": "'bring back' 是动词短语，意为'带回、勾起'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/z2xPyUuxSDLRaiPak5ADpD.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s3",
      "text": "Do you have any favourite food memories?",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p1",
      "tr": "你有什么最喜欢的食物记忆吗？",
      "g": "助动词 (Do) + 主语 (you) + 谓语 (have) + 宾语...",
      "d": "一般疑问句结构。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ErWZYFySwVCUuinoMVozKX.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s4",
      "text": "Mine start with my mother.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p2",
      "tr": "我的记忆始于我的母亲。",
      "g": "主语 (Mine) + 谓语 (start) + 介词短语",
      "d": "'Mine' 指代 'My food memories'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/yYshy9y2enC8ArsEqS8Mr6.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s5",
      "text": "She can do magic in the kitchen: Tofu and beef become red, hot mapo tofu; carrots and mutton become lovely dumplings; a big fat hen becomes a pot of warm chicken soup; even eggs and green onions become wonderful pancakes.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p2",
      "tr": "她在厨房里能变魔术：豆腐和牛肉变成红辣的麻婆豆腐；胡萝卜和羊肉变成可爱的饺子；一只肥硕的母鸡变成一锅热腾腾的鸡汤；甚至鸡蛋和葱也能变成美味的煎饼。",
      "g": "主句 + 冒号 + 举例",
      "d": "冒号后使用排比句式 'A become B' 列举了母亲的烹饪魔法。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ymtKsAHr44uzKEvPvA44AH.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s6",
      "text": "I always grow hungry thinking of them!",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p2",
      "tr": "一想到它们，我总是觉得饿！",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 (grow) + 形容词 (hungry) + 分词短语",
      "d": "'thinking of them' 是现在分词作伴随状语。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/mpSN8GmboYj9NURsR8njbf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s7",
      "text": "But my favourite food is porridge.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "但我最喜欢的食物是粥。",
      "g": "连词 (But) + 主语 + 系动词 (is) + 表语",
      "d": "转折句，引出文章核心对象。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/CmZBo9z7H3KteYFJF5jcqG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s8",
      "text": "I often wake up to the smell of porridge.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "我经常在粥的香味中醒来。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 (wake up) + 介词短语",
      "d": "'wake up to...' 意为'醒来时感觉到...'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/U8Cy8JfsxLD4ToSkXVknVE.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s9",
      "text": "Sometimes, it's sweet eight-treasure porridge.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "有时，它是甜甜的八宝粥。",
      "g": "副词 + 主语 (it) + 系动词 (is) + 名词短语",
      "d": "'eight-treasure' 是合成形容词。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/cYuSCaqYotKZNFVieWsjuf.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s10",
      "text": "Other times, it's porridge with pork and thousand-year-old eggs.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "其他时候，它是皮蛋瘦肉粥。",
      "g": "副词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 名词短语",
      "d": "'thousand-year-old eggs' 指皮蛋。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/k3zMfWhS2V4ZpDsAaKN7XG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s11",
      "text": "Each kind of porridge tastes great in its own way.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "每种粥都有其独特的美味。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 (tastes) + 形容词 + 短语",
      "d": "'in its own way' 意为'以它自己的方式'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/thdsx6gF4NMGWsihJBsH3n.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s12",
      "text": "When I fall ill, my mother always makes plain rice porridge for me.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "当我生病时，母亲总是为我做白米粥。",
      "g": "时间状语从句 (When...) + 主句",
      "d": "'fall ill' 意为生病，系表结构。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/yEF6yaULYbqKUNQY8Fnf7Q.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s13",
      "text": "That's the simplest food on any Chinese menu.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "那是任何中国菜单上最简单的食物。",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 最高级形容词 + 名词",
      "d": "'simplest' 是最高级形式。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/7byRBbeNE76PfbxdY9vnAT.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s14",
      "text": "For me, however, it's the best food in the world.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "然而对我来说，它是世界上最好的食物。",
      "g": "介词短语 + 副词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 名词",
      "d": "'however' 作插入语表示转折。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/gifB3fzMELnbdtYUvLtfCT.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s15",
      "text": "And it's better medicine than a pill!",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p3",
      "tr": "它比药片更管用！",
      "g": "主语 + 谓语 + 比较级形容词 + 名词 + than...",
      "d": "比较级结构 'better... than...'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/o3M6NNXEDuxYFXMbRFbxph.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s16",
      "text": "Now I'm studying away from home.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p4",
      "tr": "现在我在外地求学。",
      "g": "副词 + 主语 + 谓语 (am studying) + 状语",
      "d": "现在进行时描述当前状态。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/HfkxwxJHenk5WPFw7YZRCS.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s17",
      "text": "But all the warm memories stay with me.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p4",
      "tr": "但所有温暖的记忆都留在我身边。",
      "g": "连词 + 主语 + 谓语 + 介词短语",
      "d": "拟人化表达，记忆'stay with me'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/ecPYg6iJQYYbFYqxCM5nyG.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s18",
      "text": "The old days still feel so sweet in my heart.",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p4",
      "tr": "往昔的日子在我心中依然如此甜蜜。",
      "g": "主语 + 系动词 (feel) + 形容词 + 短语",
      "d": "'feel' 是系动词，接形容词 'sweet'。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/q9iEhUXf8V5QGrczVrrqja.mp3"
    },
    {
      "id": "u8-article-s19",
      "text": "What food remains strong in your memory?",
      "paragraphId": "u8-article-p4",
      "tr": "什么食物在你记忆中印象深刻？",
      "g": "疑问代词 + 名词 + 谓语 + 形容词...",
      "d": "特殊疑问句。",
      "audioUrl": "https://musk-online.fbcontent.cn/pub-musk-ai-studio/workflow/file/audio/Y4FVAZVWj5iFX7jVHMoHCW.mp3"
    }
  ],
